      "width": 560,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Migration Notes\n\nDocument explicit, reversible evolution for:\n\n- primitive-to-view default changes\n- fallback ladder changes\n- new dedicated view-role primitives\n- override rules for authors\n- compatibility behavior for legacy `ui-view` references\n\nMigration notes must preserve portability and avoid silent consumer/view drift.",
