    {
      "id": "primitive-view-consumption-schema-human-notes",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "12. Human Notes",
      "position": {
        "x": -2454.360101065393,
        "y": -2298.1666666666665
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 280,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Human Notes\n\nUse this contract to trim old graphs rather than endlessly patching ad hoc `sourceNodeId` choices. The goal is to make primitive consumption predictable:\n\n- `port` -> `port-view`\n- `bridge` -> bridge-native renderer, icon identity fallback\n- `node` -> `node-view`\n- `document` -> `document-view`\n- `summary` -> legacy compatibility fallback\n- `editor` -> `editor-view`\n- semantic far-zoom identity -> `icon-view`",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
